public class AppGluAsyncTaskCompat<Result>
extends AsyncTaskCompat<Void,Void,Result>

Extension of Android's Ice Cream Sandwich port of AsyncTask to add onException(Exception) and onFinished(boolean) callbacks.

1.0.0
